  </div>
 <div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7330">
<p>Identify competitive and alternative offerings in the market. Assess their strengths and weaknesses. Develop a strategy for winning against the competition.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7335">
<p>
Illustrate the vision and key phases of deliverables for the product. The roadmap is a plan, not a commitment.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7340">
<p>
Focus your teams' creative spirit on solving market problems by leveraging your organization's distinctive competencies.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7345">
<p>
Articulate and prioritize personas and their problems so that the appropriate products can be built.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7352">
<p>
Ensure that all departments are prepared for new product releases and all items are completed to launch the product externally.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7356">
<p>
Align your organization's selling process to the buying process, describing the key personas' information needs for each step in the process.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7361">
<p>
Produce standard product presentations and demo scripts that can be used by the sales team in a typical sales process.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7331">
<p>Inventory your assets (technical, skills, services, patents, other) and determine ways that they can be leveraged.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7346">
<p>
Illustrate market problems in a "story" that puts the problem in context. Use scenarios are one component of requirements.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7353">
<p>
Create and deliver thoughtful information (webinars, blogs, eBooks, etc.) to influence customers, buyers, industry specialists, research analysts, key editors in the press and other third parties.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7357">
<p>
Create collateral for buyer personas focused on a specific step of the buying process.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7362">
<p>
Deliver product information to qualified buyers in support of existing sales efforts.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7347">
<p>Manage proactive communications with relevant stakeholders from strategy through execution.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7354">
<p>
Develop a lead generation process that is designed to generate and nurture qualified leads with an objective to turn prospects into satisfied customers.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7358">
<p>
Create tools for salespeople focused on a specific step of the selling process.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7363">
<p>
Provide product and market expertise for events such as conferences, tradeshows, webinars and seminars.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7355">
<p>
Identify customers who are willing to give testimonials, be featured in case studies, or agree to be a reference account.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7359">
<p>
Design and deliver training programs to help the sales channels focus on how to sell the product, not how to use it.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7364">
<p>
Provide ongoing support for the sales channel. Look for opportunities to make support more repeatable.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7329">
<p>
Articulate and leverage the organization's unique abilities to deliver value to the market.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7334">
<p>
Integrate products into a coherent portfolio of products focused on the market. Manage the portfolio like a "product" (business plan, positioning, buying process, market requirements and marketing plan).</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7339">
<p>
Monitor and analyze key performance indicators to determine how well the product is performing in the market, how it impacts the company operations, and ultimately, how it contributes to profit.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7344">
<p>
Define the archetypical users of your products or services.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7351">
<p>
Measure and tune product marketing programs to ensure alignment with corporate goals.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7328">
<p>
Understand why recent evaluators of the product did or did not buy and what steps they took in the buying process.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7333">
<p>
Determine which channels best align with your markets' buying preferences.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7338">
<p>
Determine the most effective way to deliver a complete solution to an identified market problem. Where you have gaps in your offering, analyze whether to buy, build, or partner to complete the solution for your market.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7343">
<p>
Define the archetypical buyers involved in the purchasing of your products and services.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7350">
<p>
Define the specific plans and budgets for ensuring customer loyalty as well as selling products and services to existing customers.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7327">
<p>Discover problems in the market by interviewing customers, recent evaluators and untapped, potential customers. Validate urgent problems to show their pervasiveness in the market.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7332">
<p>
Map needs with target markets and analyze the market segments to actively pursue. Ensure that the targeted segments are large enough to support the current and future business of the product.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7337">
<p>
Establish a pricing model, schedules, guidelines and procedures.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7342">
<p>
Research and document the buying process your target personas use to select a product. Understand the barriers that buyers encounter during their selection process.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7349">
<p>
Define the specific plans and budgets for selling products and services to new customers.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7336">
<p>
Perform an objective analysis of a potential market opportunity to provide a basis for investment. Articulate what you learned in the market and quantify the risk, including a financial model.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7341">
<p>
Describe the product by its ability to solve market problems. Create internal positioning documents that will be used to develop external messages focused on each key buyer or persona.</p>
</div>
<div class="framework__description"
 data-toggle-hover-content="true"
 data-toggle-hover-index="7348">
<p>
Articulate the strategies and tactics for generating awareness and leads for the upcoming fiscal period, including key programs and events with measurements and goals.</p>
</div>
 </div>
